---

<section id="report" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Laporkan Situs
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Bantu kami meningkatkan layanan DNS dengan melaporkan situs judi, konten
        dewasa yang belum diblokir atau situs legal yang terblokir (false
        positive) melalui GitHub.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Report Types -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Report Unblocked Gambling Sites -->
      <div class="card p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-pink-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Situs Judi Belum Diblokir
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Laporkan situs judi yang masih bisa diakses
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Jika Anda menemukan situs judi online, slot, atau togel yang masih
            bisa diakses menggunakan DNS kami, silakan laporkan untuk segera
            diblokir.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">
              Informasi yang Diperlukan:
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-red-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• URL lengkap situs judi</li>
              <li>• Jenis permainan (slot, togel, casino, dll)</li>
              <li>• Screenshot sebagai bukti (opsional)</li>
              <li>• Waktu akses situs tersebut</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/akbxr/dns/issues/new?template=block-request.md&title=[BLOCK]%20Situs%20Judi%20Belum%20Diblokir&labels=gambling,block-request"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M12.395 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.45-.385c-.345.23-.614.558-.822.88-.214.33-.403.713-.57 1.116-.334.804-.614 1.768-.84 2.734a31.365 31.365 0 00-.613 3.58 2.64 2.64 0 01-.945-1.067c-.328-.68-.398-1.534-.398-2.654A1 1 0 005.05 6.05 6.981 6.981 0 003 11a7 7 0 1011.95-4.95c-.592-.591-.98-.985-1.348-1.467-.363-.476-.724-1.063-1.207-2.03zM12.12 15.12A3 3 0 017 13s.879.5 2.5.5c0-1 .5-4 1.25-4.5.5 1 .786 1.293 1.371 1.879A2.99 2.99 0 0113 13a2.99 2.99 0 01-.879 2.121z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Laporkan Situs Judi
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Report Adult Content Sites -->
      <div class="card p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 2a4 4 0 00-4 4v1H5a1 1 0 00-.994.89l-1 9A1 1 0 004 18h12a1 1 0 00.994-1.11l-1-9A1 1 0 0015 7h-1V6a4 4 0 00-4-4zM8 6a2 2 0 114 0v1H8V6z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Lapor Situs Pornografi
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Laporkan situs dewasa yang masih bisa diakses
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Jika Anda menemukan situs pornografi yang masih bisa diakses
            menggunakan DNS kami, silakan laporkan untuk segera diblokir.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-pink-50 border border-pink-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-pink-800 mb-2">
              Informasi yang Diperlukan:
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-pink-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• URL lengkap situs dewasa</li>
              <li>• Jenis konten (pornografi, dating dewasa, dll)</li>
              <li>• Waktu akses situs tersebut</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/akbxr/dns/issues/new?template=block-request.md&title=[BLOCK]%20Konten%20Dewasa%20Belum%20Diblokir&labels=adult-content,block-request"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pink-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M10 2a4 4 0 00-4 4v1H5a1 1 0 00-.994.89l-1 9A1 1 0 004 18h12a1 1 0 00.994-1.11l-1-9A1 1 0 0015 7h-1V6a4 4 0 00-4-4zM8 6a2 2 0 114 0v1H8V6z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Laporkan Konten Dewasa
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Report False Positive -->
      <div class="card p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Situs Legal Terblokir
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Laporkan situs legal yang terblokir</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Jika situs legal atau penting terblokir secara tidak sengaja (false
            positive) dan mengalami masalah, silakan laporkan untuk segera
            diperbaiki.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">
              Informasi yang Diperlukan:
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• URL lengkap situs yang terblokir</li>
              <li>• Deskripsi fungsi/tujuan situs</li>
              <li>• Alasan mengapa situs ini penting</li>
              <li>• Screenshot error message (opsional)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/akbxr/dns/issues/new?template=false-positive.md&title=[FALSE%20POSITIVE]%20Situs%20Legal%20Terblokir&labels=false-positive,unblock-request"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V8zm8 0a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1V8zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          Laporkan Situs Legal
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Community Guidelines -->
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12"
    >
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-2xl mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 text-black"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          >
            <path
              d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Panduan Komunitas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Dengan melaporkan situs, Anda membantu meningkatkan keamanan internet
          untuk semua pengguna.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Verifikasi Akurat
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Pastikan informasi yang dilaporkan akurat dan dapat diverifikasi
            untuk direview.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V8zm8 0a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1V8zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Respons Cepat
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Kami berusaha merespons laporan dalam 24-48 jam dan mengambil
            tindakan yang diperlukan.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Kolaborasi Komunitas
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Laporan Anda membantu melindungi jutaan pengguna internet dari
            konten berbahaya.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- GitHub Stats -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-sm border border-gray-200"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 mr-2"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M12.395 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.45-.385c-.345.23-.614.558-.822.88-.214.33-.403.713-.57 1.116-.334.804-.614 1.768-.84 2.734a31.365 31.365 0 00-.613 3.58 2.64 2.64 0 01-.945-1.067c-.328-.68-.398-1.534-.398-2.654A1 1 0 005.05 6.05 6.981 6.981 0 003 11a7 7 0 1011.95-4.95c-.592-.591-.98-.985-1.348-1.467-.363-.476-.724-1.063-1.207-2.03zM12.12 15.12A3 3 0 017 13s.879.5 2.5.5c0-1 .5-4 1.25-4.5.5 1 .786 1.293 1.371 1.879A2.99 2.99 0 0113 13a2.99 2.99 0 01-.879 2.121z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/akbxr/dns"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-gray-800 font-medium">GitHub: github.com/akbxr/dns</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Pertanyaan Umum
      </h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Berapa lama proses review laporan?
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Kami berusaha mereview setiap laporan dalam 24-48 jam. Update
              blocking/unblocking biasanya diterapkan dalam 1-2 hari kerja.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Apakah perlu membuat akun GitHub?
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Ya, Anda perlu akun GitHub gratis untuk membuat issue. Ini
              membantu kami melacak progress laporan dan berkomunikasi dengan
              pelapor.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Bagaimana jika situs sudah dilaporkan?
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Cek dulu di GitHub Issues apakah situs sudah dilaporkan. Jika
              belum, silakan buat laporan baru. Jika sudah ada, Anda bisa
              menambahkan komentar.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Apakah ada reward untuk pelapor?
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Saat ini belum ada reward material, tapi kontribusi Anda sangat
              berharga untuk keamanan internet dan akan diakui di kontributor
              list.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
